snippet.title: Saints Row 4 Official Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
Discover the climatic chapter of the saga that changed all the rules and blew the minds of a generation ! Join us on Facebook http://FB.com/GameNewsOfficial & http://twitter.com/gamenewstrailer. Check out the first official teaser trailer for Saints Row 4 ! Sexy, violent, explosive and fun !

Saints Row 4 Official Trailer (HD). Release date : August 23, 2013 for PS3 and Xbox 360 ! Subscribe now to get the latest game trailer, gameplay teaser & video, videogame walkthrough and ingame videos with Game News Official (GameNews) ! Saints Row 4 Trailer.
